=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone\" title=\"Cut Stone\"><img alt=\"Cut Stone.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cut_Stone.png?c2eb47\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boards\" title=\"Boards\"><img alt=\"Boards.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Boards.png?79a528\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oinc\" title=\"Oinc\"><img alt=\"Oinc.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Oinc.png?bf1bac\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>30</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Key_to_the_City\" title=\"Key to the City\"><img alt=\"Key to the City.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Key_to_the_City.png/42px-Key_to_the_City.png?775850\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Slanty_Shanty\" title=\"Slanty Shanty\"><img alt=\"Slanty Shanty.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Slanty_Shanty.png?7240e1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone\" title=\"Cut Stone\"><img alt=\"Cut Stone.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cut_Stone.png?c2eb47\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Worker\" title=\"Pig Worker\"><img alt=\"Pig Worker.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pig_Worker.png/42px-Pig_Worker.png?f06d7c\" width=\"42\" height=\"62\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oinc\" title=\"Oinc\"><img alt=\"Oinc.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Oinc.png?bf1bac\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Cut Stone was used to build <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Box\" title=\"Ice Box\">Ice Boxes</a> before being replaced with <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gears\" title=\"Gears\">Gears</a>.</li>\n<li>In <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Reign of Giants\">Reign of Giants</a></i>, players use Cut Stone instead of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boards\" title=\"Boards\">Boards</a> in some recipes. This is to keep some structures and items nonflammable.</li>\n<li>In the old research system, the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Research_points_list\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Research points list\">research cost</a> of a Cut Stone was 30.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_cutstone.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_cutstone.png/120px-CD_cutstone.png?8f7fcd\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div></div>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DST-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone#DST-0\">DST</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DS-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone#DS-0\">DS</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"RoG-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone#RoG-0\">RoG</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"SW-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone#SW-0\">SW</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Ham-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Stone#Ham-0\">Ham</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n <p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
